  <title>How Xanthomonas type III effectors manipulate the host plant</title>
  <URL>https://cn.bing.com/academic/profile?id=e018a4bc6b38197a33070179475a91c0&amp;encoded=0&amp;v=paper_preview&amp;mkt=zh-cn</URL>
